title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 29)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Occasionally someone will ask me if I can find a particular album that they're looking for.  After a little research, I'll discover that I've already shared that requested album in a previous bundle.  And perhaps they simply overlooked it.

With that in mind, I thought it might be helpful to compile a list of everything that has been torrented so far this year.  So, posted in the thread below, will be an alphabetical listing of what is available in all 29 bundles for 2014.

ROCK: Anberlin, Embracing Silence, Michael James Band.  CONTEMPORARY: Anthem Lights, Kim Dexter, Lindsay McCaul, Paul Demer.  ALTERNATIVE: The Artist One, Michael Hodo.  INSTRUMENTAL: Brandon Matuja.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: Calie Garrett, Leeland.  HARDCORE/METAL: Crossfire, I The Breather.  HIP-HOP/RAP: D-Tropp, DJ I Rock Jesus, DJ Official, Kris Noel, Mr Del, Ray Free, Viktory.  BLUEGRASS: Easter Brothers.  R&B:: Freshwind Worship.  POP: Holly Starr, Melanie Penn.  GOSPEL: John Hagee Family.  INDIE: Jon Guerra.  SINGER-SONGWRITER: Stephen Hample, TJ Ono.  FOLK: The Taylors.  PUNK: True Liberty.  FUNK: Various.

Our year-to-date count is now up to 1,043.
